    <string>Kai listens for voice commands only while you have voice activation enabled.</string>
    <key>NSSpeechRecognitionUsageDescription</key>
    <string>Kai transcribes your speech to understand voice commands.</string>
    <key>NSAppleEventsUsageDescription</key>
    <string>Kai controls Safari and other apps you ask it to operate, under your approval.</string>
    <key>NSDesktopFolderUsageDescription</key>
    <string>Kai organizes files in folders you ask it to manage.</string>
    <key>NSDocumentsFolderUsageDescription</key>
    <string>Kai organizes and reads documents you ask it to manage.</string>
    <key>NSDownloadsFolderUsageDescription</key>
    <string>Kai organizes downloads when you ask it to.</string>
